&lt;h2 id="workflow-of-ai-in-project-management"&gt;Workflow of AI in Project Management&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Understanding how AI integrates into project management processes can help teams leverage its full potential. Below is a simplified workflow illustrating how AI can enhance project management tasks:&lt;/p&gt;
